  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Say hello to your desktop cat — it stays in one place but keeps itself busy with adorable little actions!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Use</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag to move the cat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mouse wheel to resize</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click to rotate 45 degrees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Middle-click to change the cat's behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right-click to open the menu</p></li></ul>",
